两枚「HUAWEI NETGPT」商标，国际分类为科学仪器、网站服务，当前商标状态为申请中。此外，华为已成功注册多枚「盘古」「PANGU」商标。 市场方面，ChatGPT 概念活跃，截至 6 月 5 日 13 点 59 分，ChatGPT 概念板块指数报 1698.253 点，涨幅达 2%，成交 545.60 亿元，换手率 4.11%。 此前，据中国证券报，5 月 26 日，在中关村论坛现场，针对中国证券报记者提问华为是否有信心去承载 ChatGPT 这类规模的应用，华为昇腾计算业务 CTO 周斌回应称，完全没有问题。「我们已经服务了国内几十家合作伙伴的大模型，至少从底层技术软硬件的规模上来讲，华为不比 ChatGPT 少，ChatGPT 所需的算力需求，我们已经经过了大规模验证，是完全没问题的。」周斌表示。华为版 ChatGPT 要来了？已申请商标！华为：底层技术不比 ChatGPT 少，算力完全没问题！ | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3ff67c51d3a42f7cf9bbbb41192721c8_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604871143"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IiJeZm4ip+4dREAMaCDk2Njk1ODk1IK+W9qMGMDc4lgNAEXIJNjA0ODcxMTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1686013755.9555185", "card_id": "Q_604251906", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 299}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待哔哩哔哩上架的《成龙历险记》重新配音前 13 集，并删除了旧版的几十万弹幕？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3ea9040b49c04a564faf594bf3064796_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604251906"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IiJeZm4ip+4dREAMaCDk2NTU4NDk3IOi64aMGMCE4kQZAEnIJNjA0MjUxOTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1686013755.956662", "card_id": "Q_604528233", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 77}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年人工智能成为热门产业，电子信息专业今年会成为高考报考的「爆款」方向吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-959f2c07ffdba3aa4b10de4d926d849f_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "31 万热度", "font_colo